The paper proposes a method for logo recognition using deep learning, which involves region proposal and CNN classification. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the Computer Vision (cs.CV) and Machine Learning (cs.LG) sub-categories. Additionally, the paper involves experiments on data augmentation and training choices, which could also fall under Multimedia (cs.MM), Information Retrieval (cs.IR), and Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories.
